      "content": "wait, a hypothetical bill? i thought there was a big debate going on about the proposed changes in the recent budget talks. anyway, when economists talk about these kinds of tax cuts affecting the top tier, is there a consensus on whether it actually helps the economy overall through growth, or is that just a theory that doesn't really hold up in practice?",
